**Configuration of StatefulSet**

### statefulsetsql.yaml

``` 
   apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: StatefulSet
metadata:
  name: mysql1
spec:
  serviceName: mysql
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: mysql1
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: mysql1
    spec:
      terminationGracePeriodSeconds: 10
      containers:
      - name: mysql1
        image: mysql:5.7
        ports:
        - containerPort: 3306
        volumeMounts:
        - name: mysql-store
          mountPath: /var/lib/mysql
        env:
        - name: MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD
          valueFrom:
            secretKeyRef:
              name: mysql-password
              key: MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD
  volumeClaimTemplates:
  - metadata:
      name: mysql-store
    spec:
      accessModes: ["ReadWriteOnce"]
      storageClassName: "pd-standard"
      resources:
        requests:
          storage: 5Gi

```
